		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64230176"><p>Apparently there are metals that resist embrittlement, which is a problem in fission reactors as well.</p><p><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Neutron_embrittlement#Embrittlement_in_Nuclear_Reactors" title="wikipedia.org">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/...</a> [wikipedia.org]</p></div>
